**SECURITY.md (private reporting channel)**
- Reporting: Please email [your-security-email] or open a private security advisory via GitHub â€œSecurity > Report a vulnerability.â€
- Scope: Parser, VM, compression, converters. Do not submit exploits publicly.
- SLA: We aim to respond within 5 business days and coordinate disclosure timelines.

**CONTRIBUTING.md (IP-aware minimal)**
- Code style: Match existing Python formatting; add targeted tests.
- Commit messages: Reference files and rationale clearly.
